Bonekickers
Tue 15 Jul, 9:00 pm - 10:00 pm 60mins

2/6. Warriors.

The discovery of 18th Century bones in the Bristol Channel brings to light an extraordinary conspiracy. Anyone who has investigated the final journey of The Somerset ship in the last two hundred years has died in suspicious circumstances. Black Presidential candidate Senator Joy and Dr Adabankah, an academic from Ghana, arrive in Bath. But what are their motives, and who can the team trust? Also in HD. Contains scenes of moderate violence. [AD,S]
